2.name: source
2.textString:
$ F = m \times a$

    $= m \times \frac{\Delta v}{\Delta t}$

    $= m \times \frac{v_1 - v_0}{t_1 - t_0}$

$v_1 = \frac{F \times t_0 - t_1}{m} + v_0$

      $= a \times t_0 - t_1 + v_0$
